                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@SaileshD Yes, I know. That is what I said in &lt;a href=&quot;https://stackoverflow.com/questions/461203/when-to-use-virtual-destructors/23723229?noredirect=1#comment67336865_23723229&quot;&gt;my comment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

